### Authentication Tests
### Test đăng ký, đăng nhập, verify token

@gatewayUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Register Customer Account
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "password": "Customer@123456",
  "fullName": "Nguyễn Văn A"
}

### 2. Register Admin Account (for testing)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Admin@123456",
  "fullName": "Admin User"
}

### 3. Login Customer
# @name loginCustomer
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "password": "Customer@123456"
}

### 4. Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Admin@123456"
}

### 5. Get Current User Info
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{loginCustomer.response.body.accessToken}}

### 6. Verify Token
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{loginCustomer.response.body.accessToken}}"
}

### 7. Refresh Token
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{loginCustomer.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

### 8. Login với sai password (expect 401)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "password": "WrongPassword123"
}

### 9. Login với email không tồn tại (expect 401)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "notexist@test.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}